commit b92b08dc1f9d9ffd4c84a68d21ccb08dfe85a1c8
Author: Sebastian Utz <su@rtme.net>
Date:   Mon Oct 7 14:53:20 2024 +0200

    Fix role granting to not loose existing privileges.
    
    If a role is granted of another role, it's privileges must remain.
    
    Fixes #16710.
    
    (cherry picked from commit adf9854bdb9cbf08dde206c0a1e005a5ea3379c9)
    
    # Conflicts:
    #       server/src/main/java/io/crate/role/Role.java
    #       server/src/main/java/io/crate/role/metadata/RolesMetadata.java
    #       server/src/test/java/io/crate/role/TransportRoleActionTest.java

